l it follow your lead, or will it run away out of fear? It\u2019s all up to you.\n\nIt is time to enter the sewer.", "short_description": "You are a rat. Enter the sewer system and help a fellow rat escape what lurks within it."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.termsfeed.com/live/1b7bff2b-076c-44a2-b462-db150a651fff", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Bezbro Games", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://bezbrogames.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "1394543634671740"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "226679486946564"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "226679486946564"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1690579800, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "226679486946564"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "6973435412757189", "version": "19.93"}, "id": "744776554061767", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5664867976947279", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "6973435412757189"}, "release_statu